{"id":"1628","name":"recession-aggression-take-it-out-on-your-pillow","title":"Recession Aggression: Take It Out On Your Pillow","author":"Morgan Levy","date":"2009-03-19T11:07:00-05:00","tags":["centennial park","giant pillow fight","Nashville","pillow fight"],"categories":["Culture &amp; Arts"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2302/2202178647_5a5cf821d7.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p><p>Does the idea of beating up total strangers get you going? This weekend, if you&#x2019;ve got nothing better to do (and maybe even if you DO have something better to do), head over to Centennial Park, where &#x2013; at latest superofficialFacebookcount &#x2013; almost 800 people have RSVPed to beat each other silly&#x2026; With pillows. We missed the first giant pillow fight last September, but from the looks of the <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kWRTR783LqU\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.youtube.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">videos</a> and <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo_search.php?oid=38201697193&amp;view=all\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.facebook.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">photos</a>, it was pretty intense.</p><p>Check the <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/home.php?#/event.php?eid=38201697193&amp;ref=ts\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.facebook.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook event</a> for more details. Show up with a pillow a little before 6pm on Sunday, March 22, at Centennial park in front of the Parthenon. Just look for the 800 people with pillows.</p><p><strong>UPDATE [3/20, 2pm]:</strong> Metro PD has pulled the plug on the pillow fight because the organizers didn&#x2019;t have a permit, so don&#x2019;t show up unless you want to be escorted out by Metro&#x2019;s finest. :(</p><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2302/2202178647_5a5cf821d7.jpg?v=0\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;farm3.static.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">phillipe leroyer</a>. </em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/03/18/recession-roundup-nashvillest-guide-to-recession-deals-around-town/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Recession Roundup: Nashvillest Guide To Recession Deals Around Town\">Recession Roundup: Nashvillest Guide To Recession Deals Around Town</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2011/01/10/citywide-snowball-fight-tonight-at-6pm-centennial-park-arcticblast2011/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Citywide Snowball Fight: Tonight At 6PM, Centennial Park [#ArcticBlast2011]\">Citywide Snowball Fight: Tonight At 6PM, Centennial Park [#ArcticBlast2011]</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}